                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 6775/575.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Minister of Foreign Affairs of
                            Guatemala</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                        State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-09-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 17, 1908</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have the honor to advise your excellency that the international bureau of
                    Central American Republics was inaugurated to-day in accordance with the
                    convention signed at Washington.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Juan Barrios.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
